	<processInformation>
		<dataSetInformation>
			<common:UUID>7f401be9-d81a-45e5-8f47-381a62be5a73</common:UUID>
			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Municipal sludge treatment and disposal;dry sludge;gravity thickening</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">市政污泥处理与处置;干污泥;重力浓缩</baseName>
			</name>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification>
					<common:class level="0">Unit processes</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">End-of-life treatment</common:class>
					<common:class level="2">Waste water treatment</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Based on the data from China, the inventories on gravity thickening and agricultural use processes (i.e., electricity consumption, flocculants, wastewater disposal, and heavy metal emissions) are obtained from the best available techniques directive of sewage sludge treatment in China.These data include those directly collected from 140 wastewater treatment plants in China.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">根据中国的数据，从中国污泥处理的最佳技术指导中获得了重力浓缩和农业使用过程(即电力消耗、絮凝剂、废水处理和重金属排放)的清单。这些数据包括从中国140个污水处理厂直接收集的数据。</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
		<quantitativeReference type="Reference flow(s)">
			<functionalUnitOrOther xml:lang="en">The functional unit is the base for the treatment comparison in the life-cycle inventory. The management of one tone of dry sludge (DS) is selected.</functionalUnitOrOther>
			<referenceToReferenceFlow>3</referenceToReferenceFlow>
		</quantitativeReference>
		<time/>
		<geography>
			<locationOfOperationSupplyOrProduction location="CN"/>
		</geography>
		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">The sludge treatment and disposal steps are gravity thicking, anaerobic digestion, dewatering, and agricultural use.</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">污泥处理处置步骤为重力浓缩、厌氧消化、脱水、农业利用。</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The industrial process described pertains to municipal sludge treatment and disposal with a particular emphasis on gravity thickening, a unit process within the life cycle assessment. The process involves specifically managing dry sludge (DS), and is commonly applied in wastewater treatment plants for consolidating and thickening the sludge to reduce water content before further disposal or treatment steps.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">所描述的工业过程涉及市政污泥处理与处置，特别强调了重力浓缩这一生命周期评价中的单元过程。该过程专门涉及干污泥（DS）的管理，并且通常应用于污水处理厂，用于在进一步的处置或处理步骤之前，通过浓缩与减少污泥含水量。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="f47de995-828f-4d5d-afbb-f433b2487c29" uri="../sources/f47de995-828f-4d5d-afbb-f433b2487c29.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">HQU1bxEzOoKCLXxSxRQcDtgen4L.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
	</processInformation>
