			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">The data set users should consider this data in the context of managing one tonne of dry sludge using gravity thickening process. When comparing to other life cycle data, ensure that the functional units align. The data may not reflect alternative treatment methods or newer technologies that differ in efficiency and environmental impacts. It is advisable to account for local conditions, technological applicability, and specific regulations when applying this data in life cycle assessments.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">数据集使用者应将此数据置于使用重力浓缩过程管理一吨干污泥的情景中考虑。与其它生命周期数据进行比较时，确保功能单位一致对齐。该数据可能不反映在效率和环境影响上有所不同的替代处理方法或更新技术。在生命周期评估中应用此数据时，建议考虑本地条件、技术适用性和具体规定。</useAdviceForDataSet>
